law.text: Warehouse companies incorporated with power to guarantee warehouse receipts shall, as to the method of guaranteeing receipts, be governed by the insurance laws of this state and, as to the form of the certificate of guarantee, shall be subject to regulation of the Department of Insurance.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4768a-3.
